data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this amazing ranch style home with detached garage situated on a picturesque 5 acres with a creek bordering the rear property line all located in Prince George County.  You have endless opportunities to make this house your HOME!  Given a little TLC and you are looking at the ideal home for rural living BUT also located conveniently to I95. This quaint home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, fireplace with wood stove, detached garage, 2 pears trees and and 1 apple tree. Don't miss out call and make your appointment today!
